he startup hardening call. Remote evidence shows a clean start and proper log handling.\n\n## Issues Found\n- [ ] None. (Permission errors in the full test suite were confirmed to be environment-specific due to macOS Seatbelt restrictions and are unrelated to the changes in this task).\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\n- Successfully integrated `bootstrap_identity()` into the `narrative_api` entry point.\n- Verified that `first_boot.py` and `__init__.py` are present and up-to-date on the `cypherclaw` host to support the new identity bootstrap.\n- Service is verified operational on the live host.\n"}}
