./sdp/logs/Lead_frac-0029_1777721353.log:334:./sdp/logs/Verify_T-010_20260416T181925Z_1776384834.log:7887:+{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":"2026-04-16T23:36:18.288Z","tool_name":"write_file","tool_id":"write_file_1776382578288_0","parameters":{"file_path":"sdp/verification/t-006@20260416t181925z-verify.md","content":"# Verification Report — T-006@20260416T181925Z\n\n**Verify Agent:** Gemini CLI\n**Date:** 2026-04-16\n**Artifacts Reviewed:**\n- `my-claw/tools/senseweave/render/rules/duration_contrast.py`\n- `tests/test_duration_contrast_rule.py`\n- `my-claw/tools/senseweave/render/__init__.py`\n- `my-claw/tools/senseweave/render/rules/__init__.py`\n- `my-claw/tools/senseweave/render/pass_.py`\n\n## Correctness\nThe implementation of R4 Duration Contrast follows the requirements:\n- Log-scaled multiplier: `k * math.log(ratio)` where `ratio = length_rows / median_length`.\n- Multiplier is capped at [0.90, 1.10] (±10%).\n- `new_length = max(1, int(round(step.length_rows * multiplier)))` correctly exaggerates short vs long notes.\n\n## Completeness\n- Rule is gated to melodic roles only (`accent`, `counter`, `counter_melody`, `figuration`, `lead`, `melody`).\n- `ostinato`, `perc`, and other grid-locked roles are correctly skipped.\n- `_metadata_is_grid_locked` check is implemented and integrated.\n- Tests cover core logic, cap enforcement, and role/metadata exclusion.\n\n## Consistency\n- Follows the `RenderRule` protocol.\n- Correctly registered in `RULE_ORDER` at slot R4.\n- Uses existing `MELODIC_ACCENT_ROLES` and `GRID_LOCKED_ROLES` definitions from `metric_accent.py` (via inheritance of logic/conventions).\n\n## Security\n- No security vulnerabilities or leaked secrets detected.\n- Pure-function logic with no unsafe I/O.\n\n## Quality\n- Code is clean, well-documented with docstrings, and uses type hints.\n- Tests are comprehensive and pass in the current environment.\n- Startup hardening (`bootstrap_identity`) was verified to be pre-existing and operational via `tests/test_governor_integration.py`.\n\n## Issues Found\nNone.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\n- Implementation is solid and follows all specifications.\n- Registration in the render pipeline is correct.\n"}}
