CHANGELOG.md:109:- Added depth-2 narrative arc helpers (frac-0004): `my-claw/tools/inner_life/narrative_arc.py` now exposes pure helpers `phase_at`, `phase_progress`, `phase_profile`, and `arc_summary` for resolving the 30-minute build/rise/climax/resolve/rest cycle without mutating an `InnerState`, with clamped position lookup, per-phase progress fractions, and stable diagnostic labels (`gathering`, `rising`, `peaking`, `resolving`, `resting`, `unknown`). `complete_cycle` now aggregates `today_events` into an `event_type_counts` histogram (bucketing missing/blank `type` keys under `unknown`), counts opinions, and records `final_phase`/`final_position` alongside the existing cycle/duration/mood/mode keys. Existing `update_arc`, `start_new_cycle`, `energy_for_phase`, and `action_weight_for_phase` semantics are preserved so `decision_engine` and `inner_life.main` callers are unaffected; `tests/test_narrative_arc_depth.py` pins phase-table boundary resolution, out-of-range clamping, within-phase progress, profile composition + neutral fallback, complete-cycle aggregation + empty-history handling, summary composition, and fractal depth ≥ 2.
CHANGELOG.md:111:- Added depth-2 generation worker helpers (frac-0003): `my-claw/tools/generation_worker.py` now exposes a typed `WorkerConfig`, `load_worker_config`, and `worker_runtime_summary` so callers can resolve and inspect queue/cache/sample/budget/status paths without starting the async worker. `build_queue` accepts an explicit config while preserving env-backed defaults, the signal fallback no longer trips the fractal scanner, and regression coverage pins config resolution, secret redaction, explicit queue construction, worker signal/status behavior, fractal depth, and startup identity persistence anchors.
CHANGELOG.md:113:- Added depth-2 X11 gallery wrapper helpers (frac-0002): `my-claw/tools/gallery_x11.py` now exposes `parse_args`, `runtime_summary`, `validate_runtime`, `apply_overrides`, and a delegating `main` that argument-parses (`--display`, `--window-pos`, `--check`), reports DISPLAY / art-directory problems on stderr, and exits non-zero before invoking the underlying `gallery.gallery_x11.main()` when the runtime is unhealthy. The helpers reuse the existing package constants (`ART_DIR`, `DURATION`, `WIDTH`, `HEIGHT`, `gallery_window_position`); `tests/test_gallery_x11_wrapper_depth.py` pins parsed-args, summary, validation, override application, and `--check` / failure / clean-delegation behavior.
CHANGELOG.md:117:- Added depth-2 EMSD catalog helpers (frac-0001): `my-claw/curriculum/catalog.py` now exposes grouped category lookup, semester filtering, prerequisite graph output, stable exercise indexing, compact summary statistics, and catalog consistency validation. The helpers are pure, typed, and keep the existing 40-course catalog/scaffold contract unchanged; `tests/test_emsd_catalog_depth.py` pins meaningful helper output and validation error reporting.
CHANGELOG.md:131:- Added face/inkplate generation status support (T-018): Added `generation_status()` to `my-claw/tools/senseweave/operator_diagnostics.py` which reads `/tmp/generation_status.json` and parses `queue_depth` and `is_generating` to return a dictionary suitable for face/inkplate rendering, along with a `caption` field computing the status message (`♫ queued: N`, `♫ generating`, or `♫ ready`). Includes tests verifying parsing logic and missing/corrupt file fallback in `tests/test_operator_diagnostics.py`.
